text: Sărulești is a commune in Călărași County, Muntenia, Romania. It is composed of seven villages: Măgureni, Polcești, Săndulița, Sărulești, Sărulești-Gară, Sătucu and Solacolu. As of 2002 the population of Sărulești is 3,177 inhabitants. ==References== Category:Communes in Călărași County Category:Localities in Muntenia
title: Sărulești, Călărași
